articles.title: Divers have found wreckage, 5 remains from Osprey aircraft that crashed off Japan, US Air Force says - POLITICO
articles.description: The CV-22 Osprey carrying eight American personnel crashed last Wednesday off Yakushima island during a training mission.
articles.content:
